This paper is about using randomized value functions to drive exploration in reinforcement learning. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), control systems (cs.SY), and multi-agent systems (cs.MA). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
